room_title: Escape room "Special Ops: Mysterious Market" by The Escape Game Atlanta in Atlanta
room_address: 900 Battery Ave SE Unit 1020 Atlanta, GA 30339
room_description: You and your fellow field agents were sent to investigate the area’s local market. It’s late, it’s quiet… but something’s not quite right. Just as you are about to wrap up your inspection, you encounter a twist you never expected. Should you have seen this coming?
